          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Member Financial Transparency Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Ethics in Government Act of 1978 to require Members of Congress to file reports on transactions in securities within 7 days after such transaction and the Clerk of the House of Representatives and the Secretary of the Senate to make such reports public within 10 days.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-04-10T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
